      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Isolated the motors power supply following lockout & tag out procedure. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Marked and disconnected the power cables. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Opened the GS pump motor foundation bolts & nuts. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Using chain block lifted shifted the motor to main deck lifting area.  "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Using yard crane lifted shifted the motor to transport then send our workshop for overhauling. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Dismantled the motor, draw out the rotor and inspected the condition of motor parts. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Checked the insulation resistance of motor stator winding. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Measured Bearing housing for motor (DE: Ø 100.02 mm) measured and dimensions were within the tolerance. x 01 Pc. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Measured Bearing housing for motor (NDE: Ø 100.04 mm) was found loose, yard side carried out re-bushing and machined bearing housing cover x 01 Pc. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Supplied and renewed oil seal (45 x 68 x 12) for motor x 01 Pc."
        }
      ]
    },
